# Local dev: leave unset — the app calls /api/... and Vite proxies to your backend (e.g. port 4000).
#
# Production: REQUIRED on Netlify (or set in netlify.toml [build.environment]) — Vite bakes this in at
# `npm run build`. Without it, `/api/site-content` hits Netlify (SPA fallback), not your Render API.
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-service.onrender.com
